Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Ideal Gas Law
Formula: PV = nRT
Note:    Pressure, volume, temperature relationship for ideal gas

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Schwarzschild Radius
Formula: r_s = 2GM/c²
Note:    Event horizon radius of a black hole

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Avogadro's Number
